  "text": "The animal experiments were carried out under the Guide for the Care and Use of Animals for Research Purposes and have been approved by the Committee of the Ethics of Animal Experiments of the Zhejiang University. The source of BALB/c nude mice, the breeding condition and the operation criteria were described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . WT and OCT4A-KO (2-2 and 1-1) HeLa cells, 1×10 [CITATION_3] each, were inoculated subcutaneously into each mouse, respectively. Once the xenograft tumors were visible and touchable, the volume of the tumors was evaluated.",
